Run the test suite:

```bash
# Install development dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=code_analyzer --cov-report=html

# Run specific test
pytest tests/test_sas_metrics.py -v
```

